title: NGA. DHS, Lousiana coast boom locations as of May 14 2010, USA, May 2010
name: NGA. DHS, Lousiana coast boom locations as of May 14 2010, USA, May 2010
description: The polyline shapefile shows locations of oil booms placed near Louisiana/Alabama coast threatened by the BP's oil spill. The shapefile came from DHS's Daily Remote Sensing Situation Report of 16th May, 2010 produced in response to BP's oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico (GOM).

author.source: DHS's Daily Remote Sensing SItuation Report of 16th May 2010
